Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优良
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等很久了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,," ツギベリЧХ " Season 2   第二话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  阿真  要你花时间陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很久没单独约会了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时当家庭主妇也蛮愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是像这样约会感觉就像情侣一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夫妻又是情侣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真  你来一下好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？优良
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我拉上背后的拉链
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真  你变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以出声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说出声是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没甚么事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  阿真  让你花了这么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  以后把我的午餐费减为250就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗妳的  开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还买得起妳穿的漂亮衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…我的妄想？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不应该只让你工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我决定到餐厅打工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不需要这样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…我时间太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上我以前就想尝尝当侍应的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道我只当过上班族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是当侍应会遇到可恶的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遭受各种羞辱和引诱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不爱你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不要去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗？优良
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真你若坚持不肯  我是不会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀…倒也不是坚持不肯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,22 之 34
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忽然喊人到家里  该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想与妳共度人生  将妳介绍给我父母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不致于这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人突然去了旅行  我被留下来看家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早料到是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这里就是我们的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想干甚么都没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以马上搞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差劲  我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差劲  我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是去年圣诞节给你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一日的爱之奴隶券
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了  原来是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫做双重收入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫妻都工作  收入就增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风险也增加…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你太太恐怕是想试试穿侍应制服的滋味吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是制服这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是会激发男人的欲望吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真  你果然不了解女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子其实是喜欢穿制服的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说妳也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位先生  你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也是制服迷？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种打扮会让女人有激情的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道吗？先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太危险了  制服这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我大姐的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自拿来穿不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就想在这种情况下试试了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如我受伤住院  护士以身体来安慰我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本就是色情俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  别囉唆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我冲动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这衣服有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位吗？我带你们到坐位去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种大美女居然肯在我们店里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她看起来就像一流公司的公关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作的感觉很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这制服也好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临  请问你抽烟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不抽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的伪装太明显了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为甚么跑来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是来当客人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别妨碍我工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂  男人为甚么喜欢这种模样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裸体围裙只遮住胸部和重要部位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那若隐若现的感觉最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于只露出屁股的关系  股沟的感觉真让人受不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用说明了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳作的菜出乎意料的好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿蕃茄酱给我好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看甚么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吼呜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你干甚么？哪有人这么快又来一场的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有  大有特有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侍应  我要咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  但我的泡芙还未来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我马上去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  妳长得很漂亮  要不要跟我交往看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  竟想勾引我的优良
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还是太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨香穿甚么都好看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  你要玩几多次才满足？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天妳要当一整天的爱之奴隶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  邮件来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？是姐夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳有姐夫吗？梨香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是最近才有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  今夜太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是危机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫妻关系的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优良开始工作后就变得开朗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能阻止她  否则我就是失败的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为了我都不会穿那么短的裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都没机会看到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她竟穿上它向来餐厅的色狼絃燿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  是优良不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫她穿制服时那么好看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喊我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里坐下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是其他客人会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都睡着了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优良  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经快…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好险！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么这么快陷入妄想中？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？我的妄想已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你喜欢那种游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨香  妳怎么来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见  我是山田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳穿制服时很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳再穿姐姐的制服来一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐  妳干嘛出来打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我知道了  梨香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真是不是跟妳说了甚么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的直觉也太敏锐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真真是的  那么不信任我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不用太担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看大姐玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报酬下次再给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  电池快用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨香  谢谢妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我担心过头了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  请过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫梨香来打探我  这表示他不信任我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山本不能在今天晚上值班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有人愿意代替她？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  今天我不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我的小孩很早就会回家  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优良妳呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优良？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以拜托妳吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优良还没回来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  杏子  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她开始兼职的工作了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真出乎意料的有大男人主义倾向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想把太太一直关在家里是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优良那么漂亮  外面的诱惑肯定很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  你的问题出在过度吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优良她…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如在大部份是同性的工作地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是单独工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不会有意见是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这样女孩子会觉得无聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优良已经是大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算当了家庭主妇  所有女人都还是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子喜欢化妆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扮得漂漂亮亮的  吸引旁人的注目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不等同于外遇或勾引男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得了解她的心意才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为我了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上侍应制服接待客人是很累的劳动工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是女孩子就是会喜欢这种工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子妳也想穿制服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是没这愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳回来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机打不通  我就发电子邮件给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  电池用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没看到邮件吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:20:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我说我不担心那是骗人的  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经反省了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有充份信任妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是我对妳的爱不够深厚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算电话打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算邮件收不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的心还是相通的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗？优良
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我马上作菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约20分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你等我30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但妳要晚归的话  买预先弄好的便当就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不可以这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是新手的家庭主妇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮我剥洋葱皮好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要喝咖啡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人  你不可以那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在这里做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优良  太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.80,0:22:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优良
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了  是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.17,0:23:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.42,0:23:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不干那工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.09,0:23:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚么？可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想做好清洁和厨房的家务
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你工作累了回到家里时  我希望可以让你好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.65,0:23:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳想工作时再去做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
